</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dPZUdm cBqcmb pf-33_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eBHgEO eUYsjc pf-34_ pf-text-1"><strong>Ofsted</strong> - The Office for Standards in Education, Children's Services and Skills, responsible for inspecting and regulating services that care for children and young people.


</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eBHgEO eUYsjc pf-36_ pf-text-1"><strong>EYFS</strong> - The Early Years Foundation Stage sets the standards for learning, development, and care for children from birth to five years old.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eBHgEO eUYsjc pf-38_ pf-text-1"><strong>Safeguarding</strong> - Measures to protect the health, well-being, and human rights of individuals, ensuring they live free from abuse, harm, and neglect.


</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-jXbVAB kNtuek pf-40_ pf-r pf-c-lm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bDoQz cmNGeH pf-41_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cmaqZA fXrIOS pf-42_ pf-heading-1-h3">Steps to register with Ofsted
</h3><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cmaqZA fXrIOS pf-44_ pf-heading-1-h3">Determine the type of registration required
</h3><p class="sc-kAkozD iOjmJ pf-46_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">There are two main types of Ofsted registration for childcare providers:
</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dPZUdm cBqcmb pf-48_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eBHgEO eUYsjc pf-49_ pf-text-1"><strong>Early years register </strong>- For providers caring for children from birth to the 31st of August following their fifth birthday.
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eBHgEO eUYsjc pf-51_ pf-text-1"><strong>Childcare register </strong>- This includes the compulsory part (for children aged 5-8) and the voluntary part (for children aged 8 and over).
</li></ul><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cmaqZA fXrIOS pf-53_ pf-heading-1-h3">Meet the initial requirements
</h3><p class="sc-kAkozD iOjmJ pf-55_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Before applying, ensure you meet the following criteria:

</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dPZUdm cBqcmb pf-57_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eBHgEO eUYsjc pf-58_ pf-text-1"><strong>Suitability of premises</strong> - Your setting must be safe, suitable, and secure.



</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eBHgEO eUYsjc pf-60_ pf-text-1"><strong>Qualifications</strong> - Staff must have the appropriate qualifications, such as Level 3 in Childcare.



</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eBHgEO eUYsjc pf-62_ pf-text-1"><strong>DBS checks</strong> - All staff and volunteers must undergo Disclosure and Barring Service checks.





</li></ul><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cmaqZA fXrIOS pf-64_ pf-heading-1-h3">Complete the online application
</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dPZUdm cBqcmb pf-66_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eBHgEO eUYsjc pf-67_ pf-text-1"><strong>Ofsted online </strong>- Use the Ofsted Online portal to complete your application. You will need to provide detailed information about your setting, staff, and policies.


</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eBHgEO eUYsjc pf-69_ pf-text-1"><strong>Supporting documents</strong> - Submit required documents, including proof of identity, DBS certificates, and qualifications.


</li></ul><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cmaqZA fXrIOS pf-71_ pf-heading-1-h3">Pay the registration fee
</h3><p class="sc-kAkozD iOjmJ pf-73_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The registration fee varies depending on the type and size of the childcare provision. Ensure you check the latest fee structure on the Ofsted website.

