</h3><p class="sc-kAkozD iOjmJ pf-77_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Once your application is submitted, Ofsted will schedule a registration visit. This visit is to ensure your setting meets all necessary requirements. Prepare by:

