</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eBHgEO eUYsjc pf-82_ pf-text-1">Ensuring all policies and procedures are up-to-date and in place, such as safeguarding and health and safety policies.


</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eBHgEO eUYsjc pf-84_ pf-text-1">Conducting a risk assessment of your premises.



</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-jXbVAB kNtuek pf-86_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bDoQz cmNGeH pf-87_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cmaqZA fXrIOS pf-88_ pf-heading-1-h3">Post-registration requirements
